name: Angela Luv
description: Well, what can I say? I am a lady, who is looking for her happiness, love and understanding. And of course looking for harmony, I think that it is very important for any relationships. If I find all this in my life I will be happy to share it with my beloved person. I want to fall in love and create a happy family. I enjoy doing many things and I think that there are a lot of interesting things that I haven’t tried yet. I like my work, this is one of my main hobbies.
